---
title: Sausage and Egg Skillet with Peppers and Toast
description: This 15-min skillet is a sure-fire crowd-pleaser that's stacked full of peppers, onions and spinach! Buttery ciabatta and a drizzle of hot sauce bring this whole dish together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sausage-and-egg-skillet-f1e59447-dce41d00.jpg
